{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"40ac6d1573","title":"反对党的领导的右派言论","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d8296fe663","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"40ac6d1573"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"5b9534a58e","name":"臧学炳"},{"id":"62223ebeb6","name":"黄德元"},{"id":"ba9b59dad6","name":"张铁侠"},{"id":"cdf6939c29","name":"邓文煌"},{"id":"d518abf828","name":"阙锡成"},{"id":"f773564c0d","name":"陈作照"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b8e178f53b","type":"title","text":"反对党的领导的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"7501c0eccc","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院黄德元邓文煌张铁侠臧学炳陈作照阙锡成","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"229050c813","type":"paragraph","text":"从前没有共产党领导也没有亡国，最多不过是成半殖民地。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"68bf11f1f4","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党终归是一个政党，不是人民代表的组织，党和政府该严格分立，各级政府不应为党委所管制。我国政权的实质是一党专政，民主党派有名无实有职无权，纯属花瓶装饰。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"05ba48469d","type":"paragraph","text":"政府和党委两套人马，不需要，去党留政。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"9fa967b979","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的组织只有中央和省委就行了，制订了方针政策交各部门执行，没有党的组织，党外人士也可以贯彻。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"c436559872","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们过去迷信党中央，在每次运动中大大小小的打人事件是一贯的，上好则下(此处一字辨认不出)，这是党中央一贯怂恿的结果。(黄德元，26期学生)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"3f17479315","type":"paragraph","text":"老干部都是从山沟里跑出来的，干不了，他老先生(指毛主席)才叫实行统一战线。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"7a652bd6e8","type":"paragraph","text":"党委应在省一级有，使省一级党委领导学校的教授会。(黄德元)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"7f70c47036","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党领导不了学校就应当滚出去。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"6ebaffa8fa","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党不懂科学技术，不能领导科学工作，你们应当下台去，叫我们来搞，没有党的领导工作也能作好，实行党委制纯粹是以党代政。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"1639d522d6","type":"paragraph","text":"学校一团糟，党领导也是一团糟，河南医学院是党领导的空白点。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"5109c2dda7","type":"paragraph","text":"学生会变成了团委会的傀儡，院长是党委会的从属，班委会是党支部的傀儡。(黄德元)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"8dc0cc4fc2","type":"paragraph","text":"班委会是党支部的傀儡，不赞成党支部提出党员到团内来候选。(邓文煌，24期学生)","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"46e203532b","type":"paragraph","text":"党员不应参加青年团、工会的指导。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"1cdcbb27a9","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能盲目跟共产党走，要发挥团员的积极性。(邓文煌)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"686bef3b43","type":"paragraph","text":"咱们学校发展党员谁也不知道，三K党才秘密发展党员哩！(张铁侠，25期学生)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"a1aa84f2a5","type":"paragraph","text":"反党不等于反人民。(臧学炳，24期学生)","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"65491f1756","type":"paragraph","text":"反党不等于反人民。(陈作照)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"f706860dbb","type":"paragraph","text":"反党不等于不爱国。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"080256d769","type":"paragraph","text":"没有共产党也可以走社会主义。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"1d2162ff23","type":"paragraph","text":"团委是法西斯官僚主义，要求团政坚决分离，班委会的权力被团支部剥夺得可怜，班委会中的团员不能代表同学意见，团支部不应参加班上的学习工作。(黄德元)","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"a5bbcd1f2a","type":"paragraph","text":"学生会是团委会的傀儡，团应帮助其工作而不应统治学生会。(黄德元)","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"a601b4b015","type":"paragraph","text":"团是监视同学的机关。(阙锡成)","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"},{"id":"6445f75728","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党不好好为人民服务，我们就可打倒你们，因为没有你们，中国六亿人民也不会卖国。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573"}],"page":{"id":"c956434ebb","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"40ac6d1573","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}